*
* pvuart_cn - IP54 Paravirtual UART console driver
*
* Replaces sduart (Z85130) for the IP54 paravirtual machine.
* Uses the same PREFIX (du) and SOFT major (260) as sduart so that
* cn.c can call du_init(), ducons_write(), etc. by name and lboot
* links duinfo/dudevflag from pvuart_cn.o in place of zduart.o.
*
*FLAG	PREFIX	SOFT	#DEV	DEPENDENCIES
sfr	du	260	-	stty_ld,io

+thread_class	serial

$$$
